Package edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.util

Interface Stack<E>

Type Parameters:
E - The type of the object being stored.
All Known Implementing Classes:
ArrayStack, LinkedStack
public interface Stack<E>
An interface for creating stacks, that can be backed with LinkedLists or ArrayLists.
Author:
Sam Fishburn, Amin Mohamed, and Cooper Lentz
